FulfillRolesAction - Class in org.framed.orm.ui.action
This action is for adding to a Relation from type fulfillment the Shapess from type roletype and rolegroup ,which the source of the fufillment fulfills.
FulfillRolesAction(IWorkbenchPart) - Constructor for class org.framed.orm.ui.action.FulfillRolesAction
Constructor of FulfillRolesAction, where the id of the action and the text, which is shown for example in the context menu, is set .
FulfillRolesCommand - Class in org.framed.orm.ui.command
This command is used from the FulfillRolesAction and the RolesDialog to add all of the choosen Shapes from type roletype and rolegroups to the fulfilledRoles list of a Relation from type fulfillment and delete of the not choosen rolegroups and roleTypes from the referencedRoles list of a fulfillment.
FulfillRolesCommand() - Constructor for class org.framed.orm.ui.command.FulfillRolesCommand
Constructor of this command, where the label is set, which describes this command to the user, and initialize the oldFulfilledRoles list.
